Field.DisplayName: Do you remove it from the NT version output? - NT版出力から外すか

Field.DisplayName: Ground contact SEID - 地面接触SEID
Field.Description: SEID pronounced when contacting the ground after death. (-1: Invalid). SEID category is fixed to c - 死亡後、地面と接触したときに発音するSEID。(-1：無効)。SEIDカテゴリーはc固定

Field.DisplayName: Ground contact additional SEID (for material) - 地面接触追加SEID(材質用)
Field.Description: Additional SEID (for material) that sounds when it comes into contact with the ground after death. (-1: Invalid). SEID category is fixed to c - 死亡後、地面と接触したときに発音する追加SEID(材質用)。(-1：無効)。SEIDカテゴリーはc固定

Field.DisplayName: Number of ground contact pronunciations - 地面接触発音回数
Field.Description: Number of pronunciations when touching the ground after death - 死亡後、地面接触時に発音する回数

Field.DisplayName: Do you count the number of ground contact sounds in rigid body units? - 地面接触発音回数を剛体単位でカウントするか？
Field.Description: Do you count the number of pronunciations of surface contact after death in rigid body units? (○: Rigid body unit, ×: Character unit) - 死亡後地、面接触発音回数を剛体単位でカウントするか？(〇：剛体単位、×：キャラ単位)

Ground contact minimum impulse value - 地面接触最小力積値

Field.DisplayName: Ground contact minimum velocity value - 地面接触最小速度値
Field.Description: Minimum speed value required for ground contact determination after death - 死亡後、地面接触判定に必要な最小速度値

Field.DisplayName: Player contact SEID - Player接触SEID
Field.Description: SEID that sounds when you come into contact with Player after death. (-1: Invalid). SEID category is fixed to c - 死亡後、Playerと接触したときに鳴らすSEID。(-1：無効)。SEIDカテゴリーはc固定

Field.DisplayName: Player minimum contact impulse value - Player接触最小力積値
Field.Description: Minimum impulse value required for Player contact judgment after death - 死亡後、Player接触判定に必要な最小力積値

Field.DisplayName: Player minimum contact speed value - Player接触最小速度値
Field.Description: Minimum speed value required for Player contact judgment after death - 死亡後、Player接触判定に必要な最小速度値
